80
00:06:52,455 --> 00:06:54,857
I don't have to care about whatever you do after working hours, but─

81
00:06:54,857 --> 00:06:56,684
Right! After work─

82
00:06:56,684 --> 00:06:59,459
But stop being a pushover!

83
00:07:00,427 --> 00:07:01,839
A pushover...

84
00:07:01,839 --> 00:07:04,102
